PT Mandiri AXA General Insurance Indonesia
Career OpportunitiesThe AXA Group is one of the largest insurance groups in the world. AXA operates in more than 61 countries throughout Europe, North America, Asia Pacific, Africa and Middle East serving over 95 million customers and managing funds over Euro 1 trillion. Supported by 214,000 dedicated staff and financial advisers, AXA leads the industry in terms of professionalism, trustworthiness, innovation and reputation. AXA has a multi-distribution model in Indonesia, and due to our rapid growth we are inviting professionals to fill the following position:
Product Development Sharia
Jakarta Raya
Responsibilities:
Timely prepare registration of Sharia products to OJK.In addition, manage company's product portfolio and ensure the new business, persistency and profit targets are met in order to support company’s business plan
Requirements:Candidate must possess at least a Bachelor's Degree from a reputable university, preferably majoring in Accounting / Business.Having minimum of
3 years experience in Product Development Sharia.Have a deep knowledge in business process of Product Development Sharia.Have a good understanding in General Insurance business process.Strong analytical thinking and detail oriented
